									<span class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Google Developer Expert for Angular</span>
								</div>
								<div class="flex items-start">
									<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-500 transform rotate-45 mr-4 mt-2"></div>
									<span class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Application Security Engineer for web applications from Germany</span>
								</div>
								<div class="flex items-start">
									<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-500 transform rotate-45 mr-4 mt-2"></div>
									<span class="text-slate-600 text-lg">Organizer of germans biggest Angular Conference NG-DE</span>
